<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>FibreLife Packages | The Carpet Cleaning Company</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Explore FibreLife, FibreLife Protect and FibreLife Restore from The Carpet Cleaning Company. Professional carpet cleaning packages for commercial maintenance, protection and restorative cleaning."
  />
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg-dark:#071a16;
      --bg-dark-2:#0c241f;
      --panel:#103129;
      --panel-2:#163d33;
      --card:#ffffff;
      --text:#eaf8f2;
      --muted:#b7d2c7;
      --line:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --brand:#2fa36b;
      --brand-2:#66d19a;
      --accent:#1d7f55;
      --gold:#f3d27a;
      --shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
      --radius:22px;
      --max:1240px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Inter, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(102,209,154,0.20), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(47,163,107,0.14), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #071a16 0%, #0a211c 45%, #f4faf7 45%, #f4faf7 100%);
      color:#13241f;
    }

    a{text-decoration:none}
    img{max-width:100%;display:block}

    .wrap{
      width:min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin:0 auto;
    }

    .topbar{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:50;
      backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
      background:rgba(7,26,22,0.78);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .topbar-inner{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:18px;
      padding:14px 0;
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
      color:#fff;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:0.2px;
    }

    .brand-mark{
      width:42px;
      height:42px;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-2));
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(47,163,107,0.35);
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      color:#fff;
      font-size:18px;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .nav{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .nav a{
      color:#ddf2e8;
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:14px;
      transition:0.25s ease;
    }

    .nav a:hover{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color:#fff;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:10px;
      border:none;
      border-radius:999px;
      padding:15px 22px;
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:15px;
      cursor:pointer;
      transition:transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover{
      transform:translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-primary{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-2));
      color:#062118;
      box-shadow:0 16px 36px rgba(47,163,107,0.28);
    }

    .btn-secondary{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color:#fff;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    .hero{
      padding:72px 0 48px;
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .hero-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap:34px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding:8px 14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius:999px;
      color:#d8f1e6;
      font-size:13px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .hero h1{
      margin:0 0 18px;
      font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.7rem);
      line-height:0.95;
      letter-spacing:-1.5px;
      color:#fff;
    }

    .hero p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:18px;
      line-height:1.7;
      max-width:720px;
    }

    .hero-actions{
      display:flex;
      gap:14px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-top:28px;
    }

    .hero-points{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:32px;
    }

    .hero-point{
      padding:16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .hero-point strong{
      display:block;
      color:#fff;
      font-size:16px;
      margin-bottom:6px;
    }

    .hero-point span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.5;
    }

    .hero-card{
      position:relative;
      padding:22px;
      border-radius:28px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.11);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:auto -40px -40px auto;
      width:180px;
      height:180px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(102,209,154,0.32), transparent 70%);
    }

    .mini-label{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:8px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(243,210,122,0.12);
      color:#ffe9aa;
      border:1px solid rgba(243,210,122,0.25);
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:0.3px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }

    .hero-card h3{
      margin:0 0 8px;
      color:#fff;
      font-size:28px;
    }

    .hero-card p{
      margin:0 0 18px;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    .hero-list{
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      list-style:none;
    }

    .hero-list li{
      padding:14px 14px 14px 44px;
      border-radius:16px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color:#e8f7f0;
      position:relative;
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.5;
    }

    .hero-list li::before{
      content:"✓";
      position:absolute;
      left:16px;
      top:12px;
      width:18px;
      height:18px;
      border-radius:50%;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-size:12px;
      color:#082218;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-2));
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .section{
      padding:70px 0;
    }

    .section-head{
      text-align:center;
      max-width:820px;
      margin:0 auto 36px;
    }

    .section-head .kicker{
      color:#21764f;
      font-weight:800;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:0.18em;
      font-size:12px;
      margin-bottom:10px;
      display:block;
    }

    .section-head h2{
      margin:0 0 12px;
      font-size:clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      letter-spacing:-1px;
      color:#0d231c;
    }

    .section-head p{
      margin:0;
      color:#526a61;
      font-size:17px;
      line-height:1.75;
    }

    .packages{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap:24px;
      align-items:stretch;
    }

    .package{
      background:var(--card);
      border:1px solid rgba(16,49,41,0.08);
      border-radius:26px;
      box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(16,49,41,0.08);
      overflow:hidden;
      position:relative;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      transition:transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    }

    .package:hover{
      transform:translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow:0 24px 48px rgba(16,49,41,0.14);
    }

    .package-top{
      padding:26px 26px 22px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, #f4fbf7);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(16,49,41,0.06);
    }

    .package.badge-popular{
      border:2px solid rgba(47,163,107,0.36);
      transform:scale(1.02);
    }

    .popular-tag{
      position:absolute;
      top:16px;
      right:16px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #ffe8ae);
      color:#3a2a00;
      font-weight:800;
      font-size:12px;
      padding:8px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(243,210,122,0.22);
    }

    .icon{
      width:56px;
      height:56px;
      border-radius:18px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-size:24px;
      margin-bottom:16px;
      color:#082218;
      font-weight:800;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, #dff7ea, #c8f2db);
    }

    .package h3{
      margin:0;
      font-size:30px;
      letter-spacing:-0.8px;
      color:#0d231c;
    }

    .package .sub{
      margin-top:8px;
      color:#50685f;
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.6;
      min-height:48px;
    }

    .price-box{
      margin-top:20px;
      padding:16px 18px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:#0f251e;
      color:#fff;
    }

    .price-box .price{
      display:block;
      font-size:28px;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:-0.7px;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .price-box .small{
      color:#a8c2b7;
      font-size:13px;
    }

    .package-body{
      padding:22px 26px 26px;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:18px;
      flex:1;
    }

    .feature-list{
      list-style:none;
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .feature-list li{
      padding-left:30px;
      position:relative;
      color:#223a32;
      line-height:1.55;
      font-size:15px;
    }

    .feature-list li::before{
      content:"•";
      position:absolute;
      left:10px;
      top:-1px;
      color:#2fa36b;
      font-size:24px;
      line-height:1;
    }

    .ideal{
      background:#f3faf6;
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:16px;
      border:1px solid rgba(16,49,41,0.06);
    }

    .ideal strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:6px;
      color:#0d231c;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .ideal span{
      color:#556d64;
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.55;
    }

    .package-cta{
      margin-top:auto;
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .ghost{
      background:#eef8f2;
      color:#176a45;
      border:1px solid rgba(47,163,107,0.18);
    }

    .solid{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1f8f5d, #55c487);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(47,163,107,0.24);
    }

    .benefits{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap:18px;
      margin-top:30px;
    }

    .benefit{
      background:#fff;
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:22px;
      border:1px solid rgba(16,49,41,0.06);
      box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(16,49,41,0.06);
    }

    .benefit h4{
      margin:12px 0 8px;
      color:#0d231c;
      font-size:18px;
    }

    .benefit p{
      margin:0;
      color:#5a7269;
      line-height:1.65;
      font-size:15px;
    }

    .compare{
      background:#0c201a;
      color:#fff;
      border-radius:30px;
      padding:30px;
      overflow:auto;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    table{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse:collapse;
      min-width:760px;
    }

    th, td{
      text-align:left;
      padding:16px 14px;
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      font-size:15px;
    }

    th{
      color:#cce4d8;
      font-size:13px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:0.12em;
    }

    td{
      color:#eff9f4;
    }

    .tick{
      color:#88f0ba;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .cross{
      color:#7e9a8f;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .note-band{
      margin-top:24px;
      padding:16px 20px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color:#d7eee3;
      line-height:1.65;
      font-size:15px;
    }

    .cta-panel{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, #0d231c, #184233);
      border-radius:30px;
      padding:34px;
      color:#fff;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr auto;
      gap:24px;
      align-items:center;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta-panel h3{
      margin:0 0 10px;
      font-size:clamp(1.7rem, 3.4vw, 2.5rem);
      letter-spacing:-0.8px;
    }

    .cta-panel p{
      margin:0;
      color:#bfd8cd;
      line-height:1.7;
      font-size:16px;
      max-width:760px;
    }

    .footer{
      padding:30px 0 60px;
      text-align:center;
      color:#70877d;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px){
      .hero-grid,
      .packages,
      .benefits,
      .cta-panel{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .hero-points{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .package.badge-popular{
        transform:none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .topbar-inner{
        flex-direction:column;
        align-items:flex-start;
      }

      .nav{
        width:100%;
      }

      .hero{
        padding-top:42px;
      }

      .section{
        padding:54px 0;
      }

      .package-top,
      .package-body,
      .hero-card,
      .cta-panel{
        padding-left:20px;
        padding-right:20px;
      }

      .btn{
        width:100%;
      }

      .package-cta .btn{
        width:auto;
        flex:1 1 auto;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="wrap topbar-inner">
      <a href="#top" class="brand">
        <span class="brand-mark">F</span>
        <span>The Carpet Cleaning Company</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#packages">Packages</a>
        <a href="#benefits">Why FibreLife</a>
        <a href="#compare">Compare</a>
        <a href="#quote" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:12px 18px;">Get a Quote</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero" id="top">
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Professional carpet cleaning packages from The Carpet Cleaning Company</div>
        <h1>FibreLife packages designed to look premium and sell clearly</h1>
        <p>
          Present FibreLife as a branded carpet cleaning system with three clear service levels.
          Keep the choice simple, modern and easy to understand so customers can instantly see the
          difference between commercial maintenance, added protection and full restoration.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#packages" class="btn btn-primary">View Packages</a>
          <a href="tel:07802563213" class="btn btn-secondary">Call 07802 563213</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-points">
          <div class="hero-point">
            <strong>FibreLife</strong>
            <span>Commercial maintenance package with fast drying low moisture results.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-point">
            <strong>FibreLife Protect</strong>
            <span>Deep clean with added stain protection for longer lasting performance.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-point">
            <strong>FibreLife Restore</strong>
            <span>Premium restorative cleaning for heavier soiling and deeper recovery.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-card">
        <span class="mini-label">Recommended package layout</span>
        <h3>Make Protect your featured package</h3>
        <p>
          FibreLife Protect should sit in the middle and be framed as the most popular option.
          That gives customers a natural upgrade path and helps lift average job value.
        </p>

        <ul class="hero-list">
          <li>FibreLife is your commercial maintenance system</li>
          <li>Protect is your standout premium upgrade</li>
          <li>Restore is your specialist heavy soil and recovery option</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="packages">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="kicker">Packages</span>
        <h2>Three clear FibreLife service levels</h2>
        <p>
          Built to help customers quickly understand what each package does while making the middle option
          feel like the smartest choice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="packages">
        <article class="package">
          <div class="package-top">
            <div class="icon">F</div>
            <h3>FibreLife</h3>
            <div class="sub">Commercial maintenance cleaning for regular appearance management and fast return to use.</div>

            <div class="price-box">
              <span class="price">From £1.80 to £3.00 per m²</span>
              <span class="small">Best for routine commercial maintenance and repeat visits</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="package-body">
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li>Low moisture commercial maintenance clean</li>
              <li>Pre vacuum where required</li>
              <li>FibreLife pre treatment</li>
              <li>CRB or rotary agitation</li>
              <li>Encapsulation cleaning process</li>
              <li>Fast drying with minimal disruption</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="ideal">
              <strong>Ideal for</strong>
              <span>Offices, hotels, pubs, communal areas, managed properties and regular upkeep contracts.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="package-cta">
              <a href="tel:07802563213" class="btn ghost">Call Now</a>
              <a href="#compare" class="btn solid">Compare</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="package badge-popular">
          <span class="popular-tag">Most Popular</span>
          <div class="package-top">
            <div class="icon">P</div>
            <h3>FibreLife Protect</h3>
            <div class="sub">Deep cleaning plus professional stain protection to help carpets stay cleaner for longer.</div>

            <div class="price-box">
              <span class="price">Restore price plus protection</span>
              <span class="small">Perfect for premium domestic work and customers who want the best long term value</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="package-body">
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li>Everything included in FibreLife Restore</li>
              <li>Professional stain protection treatment</li>
              <li>Helps reduce rapid resoiling</li>
              <li>Supports easier ongoing maintenance</li>
              <li>Excellent for family homes and better carpets</li>
              <li>Premium finish with premium positioning</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="ideal">
              <strong>Ideal for</strong>
              <span>Homes with children, pets, quality carpets, landlords improving presentation and customers wanting the best overall package.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="package-cta">
              <a href="tel:07802563213" class="btn solid">Choose Protect</a>
              <a href="#benefits" class="btn ghost">Why it works</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="package">
          <div class="package-top">
            <div class="icon">R</div>
            <h3>FibreLife Restore</h3>
            <div class="sub">Premium restorative cleaning for heavier soiling, dull carpets and deeper recovery work.</div>

            <div class="price-box">
              <span class="price">From £75 first carpet</span>
              <span class="small">Commercial work typically from around £3.00 to £4.50 per m² depending on condition and size</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="package-body">
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li>Pre vacuum and detailed inspection</li>
              <li>FibreLife pre treatment</li>
              <li>Mechanical agitation into the pile</li>
              <li>Hot water extraction rinse</li>
              <li>Odour neutralising finish where required</li>
              <li>Designed for deeper restorative results</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="ideal">
              <strong>Ideal for</strong>
              <span>Domestic carpets, heavily soiled commercial areas, end of tenancy cleans and carpets needing a more intensive recovery clean.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="package-cta">
              <a href="tel:07802563213" class="btn ghost">Request Restore</a>
              <a href="#compare" class="btn solid">See Details</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="benefits">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="kicker">Why FibreLife</span>
        <h2>Sell the system, not just the clean</h2>
        <p>
          This is where you separate yourself from generic carpet cleaners.
          FibreLife should feel like a structured method with clear outcomes and clear service levels.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits">
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="icon">⏱</div>
          <h4>Fast drying options</h4>
          <p>Ideal for commercial settings where carpets need to return to use quickly with minimal disruption.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="icon">🧼</div>
          <h4>Clear service levels</h4>
          <p>Customers instantly understand the difference between maintenance, protection and restoration.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="icon">✨</div>
          <h4>Premium positioning</h4>
          <p>The naming makes your offer feel branded, specialist and more valuable than a generic steam clean.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="icon">🛡</div>
          <h4>Higher average spend</h4>
          <p>Protect gives you a natural upsell path without making the page feel pushy or overcomplicated.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="compare">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="kicker">Comparison</span>
